      "body" : "After some more testing I actually think the slowness was due to Windows being low on memory. I got the slow startup also while the USB thermometer program wasn't running, but after killing off a bunch of Google Chrome processes to get the memory usage down, Bitcoin started quickly again. I wonder if I never tested RC1 with Chrome being quite as bloated, or if something is different in RC3...",
